English:
Emergency power supply unit: <color=orange>ONLINE</color>. 
Door to <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> unlocked.
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation:
Unité d'alimentation de secours : <color=orange>EN LIGNE</color>.
Porte vers la <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> déverrouillée.

Italian.Translation:
Alimentatore di emergenza: <color=orange>ONLINE</color>. 
Porta per <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> sbloccata.

Spanish.Translation:
Unidad eléctrica de apoyo: <color=orange>ACTIVADA</color>.
La puerta a la <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> se ha desbloqueado.

Russian.Translation:
Аварийный источник питания: <color=orange>ВКЛЮЧЕН</color>.
Дверь в <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> разблокирована.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Unidade de fornecimento elétrico de emergência: <color=orange>ONLINE</color>. 
Porta para a <color=orange>ZONE 190</color> destravada.

Polish.Translation:
Awaryjna jednostka zasilająca: <color=orange>WŁĄCZONA.</color>
Drzwi do <color=orange>strefie 190 [ZONE_190]</color> odblokowane.

Japanese.Translation:
緊急電力供給ユニット：<color=orange>オンライン</color>。 
<color=orange>ZONE 190</color>へのドアの封鎖を解除。

Korean.Translation:
비상 파워 서플라이 유닛: <color=orange>온라인</color>
<color=orange>ZONE 190</color> 문 개방됨.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
緊急電源裝置：<color=orange>上線</color>。
<color=orange>ZONE 190</color>的門已解鎖。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
应急电源装置：<color=orange>在线</color>。
<color=orange>ZONE 190</color>门已解锁。
